{"tid":1547975,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"投訴小學教師網上言論違職業操守 警4職方協會去信特首","createTime":"2019-09-07T01:01:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T01:02:16.000Z","uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"20a9aadf3127cd52a5089a8637a1ac397e217dc5","tid":1547975,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:01:44.000Z","msg":"政府、警隊及警察協會多次公開譴責網民將警員及其家屬起底，但警察評議會4個職方協會周五（6日）去信特首林鄭月娥、教育局局長楊潤雄，以及元朗公立中學校友會小學校長陳志雄，投訴該校教師蔡子烯在網上散播仇恨及鼓吹校園欺凌，協會更附上該老師在網上的言論截圖。<br />\n<br />\n信中點名指責元朗公立中學校友會小學教師蔡子烯在Facebook及Instagram等網上平台公然發放針對警務人員及其子女的仇恨信息，包括惡意公開轉載、煽動他人轉載警務人員及其家人的相片及個人資料、又鼓吹於校園欺凌警察子女等。<br />\n<br />\n協會批評，為人師表理應以身作則，時刻注重自己的言行，但蔡子烯散播仇恨、鼓吹欺凌的行為，主張明顯嚴重違反教師的職業操守，認為其品格愧為人師。他們又強烈譴責蔡的不當行為，盼該校嚴肅跟進其「惡劣行徑」，不要讓學生「受到如此惡毒的敗類荼毒，更不要讓專業的教育界蒙羞」。最後更要求學校正視問題的嚴重性，「早日將離經背道的害群之馬摒除」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190907/60018439?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190907%2F60018439%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2oV%2FGdaNkEJkjxlYCjQUfm8%3D&h=5914ddb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190907%2F60018439%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=42c767a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190907/60018439?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"476c4ddc0cb0d9b05d8a5b8b9f5ee1ad8ce9e3d3","tid":1547975,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:02:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一句講晒，睇哩個post</span></span><br />\n[置頂/請廣傳/多圖] 907 遊客LOOK 暢遊大嶼山指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547426</a>"},{"pid":"74f070ba7b2f37b838b044c3b102cec3a554a9a1","tid":1547975,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:02:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}